# ðŸ“ˆ Stock Alert SMS Bot

This project monitors stock prices using the [Alpha Vantage API](https://www.alphavantage.co/).
If the stock price changes by more than **5%** between yesterday and the day before yesterday,
it fetches the latest related news from the [News API](https://newsapi.org/) and sends an SMS alert
with the top 3 headlines using [Twilio](https://www.twilio.com/).

---

## ðŸš€ Features
- Fetches daily stock prices from Alpha Vantage
- Calculates percentage change between yesterday and the day before
- If change > 5%: fetches the 3 most recent news articles about the company
- Sends SMS alerts with stock movement + headlines via Twilio
- Keeps API keys safe in a `.env` file

---

