---

## ðŸ”‘ Environment Variables
Create a `.env` file in the project root with the following:

```env
STOCK_API_KEY=your_alpha_vantage_api_key
NEWS_API_KEY=your_newsapi_key

TWILIO_SID=your_twilio_sid
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_twilio_auth_token
TWILIO_PHONE=+1234567890   # your Twilio phone number
MY_PHONE=+0987654321       # your personal phone number

Installation & Setup
1.git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repo.git
cd your-repo

2. pip install requests python-dotenv twilio

3. Add your API keys in the .env file

4. run the script